in there and get you?

299
00:27:34,587 --> 00:27:37,321
I can't have you in
a pool that's only "okay."

300
00:27:37,323 --> 00:27:39,757
It's good! It's good!

301
00:27:43,462 --> 00:27:45,295
You sure? You sure?

302
00:27:45,297 --> 00:27:47,598
I'm sure!

303
00:28:27,740 --> 00:28:30,407
