it's time to come out now.

304
00:28:30,409 --> 00:28:31,975
Just a few more minutes!

305
00:28:31,977 --> 00:28:34,044
No. You do what Pop-Pop says.

306
00:28:34,046 --> 00:28:38,382
Come on, baby, before
you turn into a prune.

307
00:30:12,845 --> 00:30:13,911
Miss?

308
00:30:13,913 --> 00:30:15,312
The gentleman
would like me to let

309
00:30:15,314 --> 00:30:17,881
you know that your
next drink is on him.

310
00:30:18,684 --> 00:30:21,084
Just let me know
when you're ready.

311
00:30:47,513 --> 00:30:49,413
I'm ready.

312
